=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides information about the data source that is used to create an ML
input channel.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> DataSource => L<Paws::CleanRoomsML::InputChannelDataSource>

The data source that is used to create the ML input channel.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RoleArn => Str

The ARN of the IAM role that Clean Rooms ML can assume to read the data
referred to in the C<dataSource> field the input channel.

Passing a role across AWS accounts is not allowed. If you pass a role
that isn't in your account, you get an C<AccessDeniedException> error.



